"Your Cutling keyboard is ready! While typing anywhere, tap the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to switch to Cutling." = "剪切片段键盘已准备就绪！在任何地方输入时，点击键盘上的🌐地球图标切换到剪切片段。";
"Follow the two simple steps below to start using your custom keyboard. This page will automatically update as you complete each step." = "按照以下两个简单步骤开始使用您的自定义键盘。完成每个步骤后，此页面将自动更新。";
"**Step 1:** Tap 'Open Cutling Settings' below, go to **Keyboards** and select **Cutling** from the list." = "**第1步：** 点击下方「打开剪切片段设置」，进入**键盘**，从列表中选择**剪切片段**。";
"**Step 2:** Make sure **Allow Full Access** is ON. This lets the keyboard copy images to your clipboard. Your data stays private and is never sent anywhere." = "**第2步：** 确保**允许完全访问**已开启。这将允许键盘将图片复制到剪贴板。您的数据始终保持私密，不会发送到任何地方。";
"**Step 3:** Tap on the text input and choose \"Cutling\" using the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to update the \"Full Access\" status." = "**第3步：** 点击文本输入框，使用键盘上的🌐地球图标选择「剪切片段」，以更新「完全访问」状态。";
"**Step 4:** You're good to go! The usage guide is provided below." = "**第4步：** 一切就绪！使用指南在下方提供。";
"While typing in any app, tap or hold the 🌐 globe key at the bottom-left of your keyboard, then select Cutling" = "在任何应用中输入时，点击或长按键盘左下角的🌐地球键，然后选择剪切片段";
"Tap any text cutling and it will be typed into your current text field immediately" = "点击任意文本剪切片段，它将立即输入到当前文本框中";
"Tap an image cutling to copy it to your clipboard, then paste it into the app you're using (usually by tapping and holding, then selecting Paste). Apple currently does not support directly pasting an image on this app." = "点击图片剪切片段可将其复制到剪贴板，然后粘贴到您正在使用的应用中（通常是长按后选择粘贴）。Apple 目前不支持在此应用中直接粘贴图片。";
"Copy any text, then tap the 'Add from Clipboard' button in the Cutling keyboard to save it as a new cutling" = "复制任意文本，然后在剪切片段键盘中点击「从剪贴板添加」按钮，即可保存为新的剪切片段";
