/* MARK: - Paste Settings (macOS) - Direct Paste opt-in */
"Paste directly into other apps" = "直接粘贴到其他 App";
"When on, picking a cutling from the hotkey-summoned picker sends a single ⌘V keystroke into the app that was frontmost, so the cutling is pasted at the cursor. Off by default. When off, Cutling copies to the clipboard and you paste manually with ⌘V." = "开启后，从快捷键唤起的选取器中选择一个剪切片段，会向之前最前面的 App 发送一次 ⌘V，从而把剪切片段粘贴到光标处。默认关闭。关闭时，剪切片段会被复制到剪贴板，需要你用 ⌘V 手动粘贴。";
"Permission" = "权限";
"Cutling uses Accessibility access only to send the ⌘V keystroke to the previously focused app after you pick a cutling. It does not read other apps' UI or control your computer." = "剪切片段仅在你选取一个剪切片段后，使用辅助功能权限把 ⌘V 发送给之前获得焦点的 App。它不会读取其他 App 的界面，也不会控制你的电脑。";
"Direct Paste" = "直接粘贴";
"Direct paste needs Accessibility access." = "直接粘贴需要辅助功能权限。";
